Jeanne Bérangère https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeanne_B%C3%A9rang%C3%A8re 0 Jeanne Bérangère (9 June 1864 – 19 November 1928) was a French stage and film actress whose career spanned nearly forty years on the stage and in films during the silent film era.
